-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
New Taylor fe space
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Put the header file
   fe_dgt.h 
in folder deal.II/include/deal.II/fe

Put the following files 
   fe_dgt.cc 
   fe_dgt.inst.in 
in folder deal.II/source/fe

In deal.II/source/fe/CMakeLists.txt add two additional file entries

SET(_src
  .
  .
  .
  fe_dgp_nonparametric.cc
  fe_dgt.cc                        <== New entry
  fe_dgq.cc
  .
  .
  .
  )

SET(_inst
  .
  .
  .
  fe_dgp_nonparametric.inst.in
  fe_dgt.inst.in                   <== New entry
  fe_dgq.inst.in
  .
  .
  .
  )

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
New reinit function in FEValues class
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Add the contents from fe_values.h into this file

deal.II/include/deal.II/fe/fe_values.h

at around line 3514.

Add contents of fe_values.cc into this file

deal.II/source/fe/fe_values.cc

at around line 3393.
